Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小葵妳去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 小葵
